      "title": "Incubator",
      "pageid": 4720,
      "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div id=\"infoboxborder\">\n<table id=\"infoboxtable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxheader\">Incubator\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding-bottom: 5px; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/File:Incubator.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Incubator.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/c/c7/Incubator.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"96\" /></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxdetail\" style=\"text-align: center; font-style: italic;\">Hatches eggs into baby chickens and ducks.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Information\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Cost:\n</td>\n<td id=\"infoboxdetail\">N/A\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n</div>\n<dl><dd><i>See also: <a href=\"/Slime_Incubator\" title=\"Slime Incubator\">Slime Incubator</a> or <a href=\"/Ostrich_Incubator\" title=\"Ostrich Incubator\">Ostrich Incubator</a></i></dd></dl>\n<p>The <b>Incubator</b> is a <a href=\"/Tools\" title=\"Tools\">tool</a> used to hatch eggs.  It comes with the <a href=\"/Coop\" title=\"Coop\">Big Coop</a> and the <a href=\"/Coop\" title=\"Coop\">Deluxe Coop</a>, where it appears to the left of the <a href=\"/Hay_Hopper\" title=\"Hay Hopper\">Hay Hopper</a>.\n</p><p>To use the Incubator, place an egg into it by left-clicking.  An egg cannot be removed once it is placed in an incubator unless the coop is at capacity.\n</p><p>If the coop is at capacity (8 animals for a Big Coop, 12 for a Deluxe Coop), the egg won't hatch until a space is freed up. This can happen by selling an animal or moving an animal to another coop. Once the coop is below capacity, entering the building will cause the egg to hatch instantly. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Incubation_Times\">Incubation Times</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Incubator&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Incubation Times\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Below are the times it takes to hatch an egg using the Incubator.\n</p><p>These times are cut in half with the <a href=\"/Farming#Farming_Skill\" title=\"Farming\">Coopmaster Profession</a>. <a href=\"/Fairy_Dust\" title=\"Fairy Dust\">Fairy Dust</a> does not work on Incubators.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable roundedborder\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Egg\n</th>\n<th>Hatches\n</th>\n<th>Processing Time<sup id=\"cite_ref-processtime_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-processtime-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120955\">.mw-parser-output .nametemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplate img,.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/26/Egg.png/24px-Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/26/Egg.png/36px-Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/2/26/Egg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Egg</a></span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Large Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5d/Large_Egg.png/24px-Large_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/5d/Large_Egg.png/36px-Large_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/5/5d/Large_Egg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Egg</a></span>\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"White Chicken.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/22/White_Chicken.png/24px-White_Chicken.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/22/White_Chicken.png/36px-White_Chicken.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/2/22/White_Chicken.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Chicken\" title=\"Chicken\">Chicken</a></span>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"5\"><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120974\">.mw-parser-output .durationtemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .durationtemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .durationtemplate img,.mw-parser-output .durationtemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"durationtemplate\"><img alt=\"Time Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/24px-Time_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/36px-Time_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/70/Time_Icon.png 2x\" /> 9,000m (5d 16h 40m)</span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Brown Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/01/Brown_Egg.png/24px-Brown_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/01/Brown_Egg.png/36px-Brown_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/0/01/Brown_Egg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Brown Egg</a></span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Large Brown Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/91/Large_Brown_Egg.png/24px-Large_Brown_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/91/Large_Brown_Egg.png/36px-Large_Brown_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/91/Large_Brown_Egg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Brown Egg</a></span>\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Brown Chicken.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/fd/Brown_Chicken.png/24px-Brown_Chicken.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/fd/Brown_Chicken.png/36px-Brown_Chicken.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/f/fd/Brown_Chicken.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Chicken\" title=\"Chicken\">Chicken</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Void Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/58/Void_Egg.png/24px-Void_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/58/Void_Egg.png/36px-Void_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/5/58/Void_Egg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Void_Egg\" title=\"Void Egg\">Void Egg</a></span>\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Void Chicken.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/67/Void_Chicken.png/24px-Void_Chicken.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/67/Void_Chicken.png/36px-Void_Chicken.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/6/67/Void_Chicken.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Void_Chicken\" title=\"Void Chicken\">Void Chicken</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Golden Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/97/Golden_Egg.png/24px-Golden_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/97/Golden_Egg.png/36px-Golden_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/97/Golden_Egg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Golden_Egg\" title=\"Golden Egg\">Golden Egg</a></span>\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Golden Chicken.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/3c/Golden_Chicken.png/24px-Golden_Chicken.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/3c/Golden_Chicken.png/36px-Golden_Chicken.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/3c/Golden_Chicken.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Golden_Chicken\" title=\"Golden Chicken\">Golden Chicken</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Duck Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/31/Duck_Egg.png/24px-Duck_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/31/Duck_Egg.png/36px-Duck_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/31/Duck_Egg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Duck_Egg\" title=\"Duck Egg\">Duck Egg</a></span>\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Duck.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/38/Duck.png/24px-Duck.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"23\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/38/Duck.png/36px-Duck.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/38/Duck.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Duck\" title=\"Duck\">Duck</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Dinosaur Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a1/Dinosaur_Egg.png/24px-Dinosaur_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a1/Dinosaur_Egg.png/36px-Dinosaur_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/a1/Dinosaur_Egg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Dinosaur_Egg\" title=\"Dinosaur Egg\">Dinosaur Egg</a></span>\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Dinosaur.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/89/Dinosaur.png/24px-Dinosaur.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/89/Dinosaur.png/36px-Dinosaur.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/8/89/Dinosaur.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Dinosaur\" title=\"Dinosaur\">Dinosaur</a></span>\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120974\"/><span class=\"durationtemplate\"><img alt=\"Time Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/24px-Time_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/36px-Time_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/70/Time_Icon.png 2x\" /> 18,000m (11d 6h 40m)</span>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Incubator&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-processtime-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-processtime_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">See <samp>Object::performObjectDropInAction</samp> in the game code.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Incubator&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6\" title=\"Version History\">1.6</a>: Brown and white eggs now always give the corresponding color of chicken, instead of choosing a chicken color randomly.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.6.4</a>: Incubated eggs can now be retrieved if the coop is at capacity.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Tools\" title=\"Tools\">Tools</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Basic\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Axes\" title=\"Axes\">Axes</a> • <a href=\"/Golden_Scythe\" title=\"Golden Scythe\">Golden Scythe</a> • <a href=\"/Iridium_Scythe\" title=\"Iridium Scythe\">Iridium Scythe</a> • <a href=\"/Hoes\" title=\"Hoes\">Hoes</a> • <a href=\"/Pans\" title=\"Pans\">Pans</a> • <a href=\"/Pickaxes\" title=\"Pickaxes\">Pickaxes</a> • <a href=\"/Scythe\" title=\"Scythe\">Scythe</a> • <a href=\"/Trash_Cans\" title=\"Trash Cans\">Trash Cans</a> • <a href=\"/Watering_Cans\" title=\"Watering Cans\">Watering Cans</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Fishing\" title=\"Fishing\">Fishing</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Training_Rod\" title=\"Training Rod\">Training Rod</a> • <a href=\"/Bamboo_Pole\" title=\"Bamboo Pole\">Bamboo Pole</a> • <a href=\"/Fiberglass_Rod\" title=\"Fiberglass Rod\">Fiberglass Rod</a> • <a href=\"/Iridium_Rod\" title=\"Iridium Rod\">Iridium Rod</a> • <a href=\"/Advanced_Iridium_Rod\" title=\"Advanced Iridium Rod\">Advanced Iridium Rod</a> • <a href=\"/Crab_Pot\" title=\"Crab Pot\">Crab Pot</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Other\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Auto-Grabber\" title=\"Auto-Grabber\">Auto-Grabber</a> • <a href=\"/Auto-Petter\" title=\"Auto-Petter\">Auto-Petter</a> • <a href=\"/Hay_Hopper\" title=\"Hay Hopper\">Hay Hopper</a> • <a href=\"/Heater\" title=\"Heater\">Heater</a> • <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Incubator</a> • <a href=\"/Milk_Pail\" title=\"Milk Pail\">Milk Pail</a> • <a href=\"/Ostrich_Incubator\" title=\"Ostrich Incubator\">Ostrich Incubator</a> • <a href=\"/Shears\" title=\"Shears\">Shears</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414005239\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.068 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.074 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3390/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4097/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 692/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 6450/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   44.993      1 -total\n 39.57%   17.802      1 Template:Infobox_tool\n 35.33%   15.896     14 Template:Name\n 32.38%   14.570      1 Template:Description\n  9.11%    4.101      2 Template:Duration\n  6.36%    2.861      2 Template:History\n  3.34%    1.502      2 Template:Version\n  2.98%    1.342      1 Template:InfoboxSEO\n  2.60%    1.171      1 Template:NavboxTools\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:4720-0!canonical and timestamp 20260414005239 and revision id 190275\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "{{Infobox tool\n|name         = Incubator\n|image        = Incubator.png\n|cost         = N/A\n}}\n:''See also: [[Slime Incubator]] or [[Ostrich Incubator]]''\nThe '''Incubator''' is a [[Tools|tool]] used to hatch eggs.  It comes with the [[Coop|Big Coop]] and the [[Coop|Deluxe Coop]], where it appears to the left of the [[Hay Hopper]].\n\nTo use the Incubator, place an egg into it by left-clicking.  An egg cannot be removed once it is placed in an incubator unless the coop is at capacity.\n\nIf the coop is at capacity (8 animals for a Big Coop, 12 for a Deluxe Coop), the egg won't hatch until a space is freed up. This can happen by selling an animal or moving an animal to another coop. Once the coop is below capacity, entering the building will cause the egg to hatch instantly. \n\n==Incubation Times==\nBelow are the times it takes to hatch an egg using the Incubator.\n\nThese times are cut in half with the [[Farming#Farming Skill|Coopmaster Profession]]. [[Fairy Dust]] does not work on Incubators.\n\n{|class=\"wikitable roundedborder\"\n! Egg\n! Hatches\n! Processing Time<ref name=\"processtime\"/>\n|-\n| {{Name|Egg}}{{Name|Large Egg}}\n| {{Name|White Chicken|link=Chicken}}\n|rowspan=\"5\"| {{duration|9,000m (5d 16h 40m)}}\n|-\n| {{Name|Brown Egg}}{{Name|Large Brown Egg}}\n| {{Name|Brown Chicken|link=Chicken}}\n|-\n| {{Name|Void Egg}}\n| {{Name|Void Chicken}}\n|-\n| {{Name|Golden Egg}}\n| {{Name|Golden Chicken}}\n|-\n| {{Name|Duck Egg}}\n| {{Name|Duck}}\n|-\n| {{Name|Dinosaur Egg}}\n| {{Name|Dinosaur}}\n| {{duration|18,000m (11d 6h 40m)}}\n|-\n|}\n\n==References==\n<references>\n  <ref name=\"processtime\">See <samp>Object::performObjectDropInAction</samp> in the game code.</ref>\n</references>\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.6|Brown and white eggs now always give the corresponding color of chicken, instead of choosing a chicken color randomly.}}\n{{History|1.6.4|Incubated eggs can now be retrieved if the coop is at capacity.}}\n\n{{NavboxTools}}\n\